        "bounding_box": {
            "x1": 164,
            "y1": 727,
            "x2": 1130,
            "y2": 882
        }
    },
    {
        "line_number": 8,
        "text": "प्रतिदिन ब्राह्मण संध्योपासन करे, यह विधि-वाक्य है ।",
        "image_path": "datasetProcessed/cropped_textlines/images/paramananda1924_08_textline_8.png",
        "bounding_box": {
            "x1": 167,
            "y1": 880,
            "x2": 1915,
            "y2": 1044
        }
    },
    {
        "line_number": 9,
        "text": "ब्राह्मण: सुरां न पिबेत् ।",
        "image_path": "datasetProcessed/cropped_textlines/images/paramananda1924_08_textline_9.png",
        "bounding_box": {
            "x1": 153,
            "y1": 1033,
            "x2": 1127,
            "y2": 1209
        }
    },
    {
        "line_number": 10,
        "text": "भी नहीं करता, वह संपूर्ण द्विज-कर्मों से बाहर करने योग्य है ।",
        "image_path": "datasetProcessed/cropped_textlines/images/paramananda1924_08_textline_10.png",
        "bounding_box": {
            "x1": 45,
            "y1": 1928,
            "x2": 2059,
            "y2": 2095
        }
    },
    {
        "line_number": 11,
        "text": "ब्राह्मण मदिरा-पान न करे, यह निषेध-वाक्य है । और मनु",
        "image_path": "datasetProcessed/cropped_textlines/images/paramananda1924_08_textline_11.png",
        "bounding_box": {
